import { Container, Card } from "react-bootstrap";

export default function Profile() {
    return (
        <Container>
            <Card className="mx-auto my-5" style={{width:"60rem"}}>
                <Card.Body>
                    <Row>
                        <Col md={9} style={{border:"1px solid red"}}>
                        </Col>
                        <Col md={3} style={{border:"1px solid red"}}>
                        </Col>
                    </Row>
                </Card.Body>
            </Card>
        </Container>
    )
}
